\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5cb387a05a23380001fc11aa.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"115\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"郑晓博讲的好吗？感觉讲的太细了你觉得呢？\", \"nickname\": \"Jasmine\", \"userid\": \"5621c6df3f95a31678555d16\", \"publish_time\": \"2020-12-08\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5e13d237a61cac00016bbf42.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"42\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"我太想改变了，我在努力！未来也会一直努力！\", \"nickname\": \"阿君阿么\", \"userid\": \"5ec9e39d0000000001001959\", \"publish_time\": \"2020-12-08\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5eed76dbccdc38000157b89b.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"32\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"我就想知道考过了之后呢，有没有找到比较满意的工作\", \"nickname\": \"一世迷離\", \"userid\": \"594a245c50c4b439b30a18d3\", \"publish_time\": \"2020-12-10\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/594a245c50c4b439b30a18d3.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"21\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"考过证的你现在在哪呀\", \"nickname\": \"大蝌蚪的吃吃life\", \"userid\": \"5854728f6a6a691c99778904\", \"publish_time\": \"2020-12-10\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/cd255d0e201935e0d852bd371f18c198.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"14\"}]', '2021-02-02 13:45:33');
