face👼\", \"userid\": \"565906a9589de354b292d2ff\", \"publish_time\": \"2020-04-27\", \"avatar\": \"//ci.xiaohongshu.com/cbc0d442-77cc-4659-9c8e-a67706f4abe4@r_320w_320h.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"2\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"求分享全部书单\", \"nickname\": \"小田一定要争气\", \"userid\": \"5c0c72ce000000000502e101\", \"publish_time\": \"01-16\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/6002c6151e633300012be6b2.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"0\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"我想问下这个金题卷和背诵版 是8月才会出版那吗 我感觉那个卖书的在骗我\", \"nickname\": \"绒儿嘻嘻哈哈\", \"userid\": \"5b52dda8e8ac2b4553641fd2\", \"publish_time\": \"2020-11-28\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5ffa9971c3a867b4deb064d4.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"1\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"准备2021 买的是2020柏浪涛刑法攻略 现在是精讲卷和 真题卷鹅\", \"nickname\": \"阿芹\", \"userid\": \"5ea1423c000000000100aa19\", \"publish_time\": \"2020-11-23\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5fd8da3bd3cff700012b027c.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"0\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"刑法攻略讲义卷和精讲卷是一个样嘛？我怎么只能搜到精讲卷\", \"nickname\": \"哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈\", \"userid\": \"5bcbff7edc614c0001e6592d\", \"publish_time\": \"2020-11-19\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5fc755e8fc46fb0001140f57.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"0\"}]', '2021-02-02 13:49:13');
INSERT INTO `lrb_note`(`id`, `note_id`, `note_url`, `title`, `video_poster`, `video_src`, `images_lists`, `content`, `like_num`, `comment_num`, `star_num`, `publish_date`, `author_name`, `author_image`, `author_id`, `description`, `board_id`, `tag_str`, `note_str`, `comment_str`, `spider_time`) VALUES (58, '5fcaf7460000000001005bbe', 'https://www.xiaohongshu.com/discovery/item/5fcaf7460000000001005bbe', '公考、法考、注册会计师、税务师备考教材攻略', 'https://ci.xiaohongshu.com/83dafbcf-3cc7-f1d3-db5e-9f425cf1a955', 'http://v.xiaohongshu.com/a9d84b2a5fffd975103f4b41211ee3f1fb251613_v1_ln?sign=adb0208bc79845c9cc31ef2d5e5bea06&t=601ac880', '', '学习之前要制定计划，计划要清晰且适度，清晰指可量化，例如每天6.30起床、每天听3结网课，每天做2结习题等，适度指目标不能超出自己的能力范围，否则自己会缺乏动力实现！每完成计划都画一个勾，培养执行力！\n.\n第一遍学习听网课➕记笔记；第二遍学习刷题；第三遍学习背诵笔记；第四学习遍回顾讲义；第五遍学习模拟考试。\n.\n6.50-7.50（背书）、12点-13点（做题）、18点-22点（学习）、22点-22.30（跑步），23点-2点（学习➕总结）\n@校园薯 @薯队长 @视频薯\n', 665, 55, 565, '2020-12-05 10:58', '一个幸运的伪学霸', 'https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5e88b37c72946e0001b3b191.jpg@240w_240h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg', '5e3bd70700000000010026b7', '学习之前要制定计划，计划要清晰且适度，清晰指可量化，例如每天6.30起床、每天听3结网课，每天做2结习题等，适度指目标不能超出自己的能力范围，否则自己会缺乏动力实现！每完成计划都画一个勾，培养执行力！', '5ea80b30000000000100791a', '[]', '[{\"note_id\": \"5fc5b20800000000010088a9\", \"note_desc\": \"两年，我考过了公考、法考、注会五门和税务师\"}, {\"note_id\": \"5eba14a6000000000101fb6d\", \"note_desc\": \"🏅那些含金量超高的证书📖\"}, {\"note_id\": \"5fc2fd8d000000000100671e\", \"note_desc\": \"CPA不管考没考过 这条视频都一定要发\"}, {\"note_id\": \"5fd5ad5e0000000001006d8f\", \"note_desc\": \"CPA打卡day8\"}, {\"note_id\": \"5fce50a100000000010049fa\", \"note_desc\": \"21年CPA备考开始啦！来一起学习吗☺️\"}, {\"note_id\": \"5fd9f038000000000101c5ce\", \"note_desc\": \"关于会计考证那些事\"}, {\"note_id\": \"5fda032800000000010087e4\", \"note_desc\": \"零基础在职过CPA学姐教你用轻一\"}, {\"note_id\": \"5fd478f9000000000101f40d\", \"note_desc\": \"你起不来，每早5点等你，走的慢但不后退！\"}, {\"note_id\": \"5ff077910000000001002783\", \"note_desc\": \"CPA6科的老师推荐！零基础适用\"}, {\"note_id\": \"5fc62ba9000000000101f109\", \"note_desc\": \"会计师事务所的加班有多可怕？\"}]', '[{\"comment_text\": \"检察院办经侦案子，需要公务员法考cpa\", \"nickname\": \"当30岁的我\", \"userid\": \"5f300cf700000000010061aa\", \"publish_time\": \"2020-12-07\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5f300cf700000000010061aa.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"8\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"身为一条咸鱼的我 男票通过了法考 注会五门 资产评估师两门 税务师四门 战略成绩还没出来(~_~;)你们都好优秀呀 向你们看齐\", \"nickname\": \"limanjuan4455\", \"userid\": \"5e5e197c00000000010034ce\", \"publish_time\": \"2020-12-15\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5e5e19981971ce0001553769.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"2\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"我是考了执业医师 ， 执业中药师 ，执业药师 ，卫生系统的药师职称，初级会计师。证书基本上都不怎么用到。今年不知道要不要考律师资格证，现在又想考公务员，还想考研究生。唉！很迷茫，亲们帮忙给个建议！不胜感激\", \"nickname\": \"蔡衍一\", \"userid\": \"5fc17dbe000000000101ed89\", \"publish_time\": \"2020-12-06\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5fc17dbe000000000101ed89.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"2\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"牛\", \"nickname\": \"无法企及的时光\", \"userid\": \"5c5642f80000000010034fa8\", \"publish_time\": \"01-30\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5c564482e0d75d000134ac2c.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"0\"}, {\"comment_text\": \"学霸您好！司考考试您分享各个老师的书，是教材？还是讲义？\", \"nickname\": \"春风十里\", \"userid\": \"5daba5f600000000010093ec\", \"publish_time\": \"01-16\", \"avatar\": \"https://img.xiaohongshu.com/avatar/5fa502718afb1f0001d34fdf.jpg@80w_80h_90q_1e_1c_1x.jpg\", \"like_num\": \"0\"}]', '2021-02-02 13:49:18');
